io.hipergateSynchronization.messageService

Class MessagingServiceFacade<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.hipergateSynchronization.messageService.MessagingServiceFacade<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMessagingService<T>

    public class MessagingServiceFacade<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMessagingService<T>
    Implementation of IMessagingService. MessagingServiceFacade is responsible for receiving and sending messages to queues. Fixed to InputQueue "FROM_HIPERGATE_TO_OPENZ" and OutputQueue "FROM_OPENZ_TO_HIPERGATE".
    Author:
    Daniel Glake, cglaeser
